      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks awesome on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a great vehicle without that brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to help you get behind the wheel!",
