    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, distinguished by its eight individual throttle bodies and a linear power delivery peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The six-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior lateral traction. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle body actuators, ensuring the double-VANOS system operates within factory tolerances. The chassis remains taut with M-specific subframe reinforcement and aluminum suspension components. While the finish reflects its service as a spirited grand tourer, the mechanical vitals and atmospheric induction note remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
